<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Reminder from Wolf Projects Manager </h1>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @project.user.email %>, Remember to attend to the <%= @project.name %> project and update each tasks till all are 100% complete
    </p>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder about <%= @project.name %> project that you created on <%= @project.created_at.strftime("%A, %B") %> (<%= @project.created_at.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>) at <%= @project.created_at.strftime("%I:%M%p") %> </p>
    <%= link_to "Wolf Projects", root_url, class: "btn btn-secondary"  %>
  </body>
</html>
